    <speech id="com.kildarestreet/seanad/2013-02-27a.387" nospeaker="true" time="12:50:00"><p>Government amendment No. 59:
In page 53, between lines 28 and 29, to insert the following subsection:&quot;(3) Section 13(2) of the Act of 2008 is amended by inserting after paragraph (c) the following:&#8220;(ca) actions to be taken relating to the objectives of the Authority under section 16(2) of the Taxi Regulation Act 2013,&#8221;.&#8221;.</p></speech>
    <speech id="com.kildarestreet/seanad/2013-02-27a.388" nospeaker="true" time="12:50:00"><p>Amendment agreed to.</p></speech>
    <speech id="com.kildarestreet/seanad/2013-02-27a.389" nospeaker="true" time="12:50:00"><p>Section 55, as amended, agreed to.</p></speech>
