    <speech id="com.kildarestreet/seanad/2013-02-27a.413" nospeaker="true" time="12:50:00"><p>Question proposed: &quot;That the Title be the Title to the Bill.&quot;</p></speech>
    <speech />
    <speech id="com.kildarestreet/seanad/2013-02-27a.415" nospeaker="true" time="12:50:00"><p>Question put and agreed to.</p></speech>
    <speech id="com.kildarestreet/seanad/2013-02-27a.416" nospeaker="true" time="12:50:00"><p>Bill reported with amendments.</p></speech>
